sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager


participant UI as Planning UI
participant BFF as Project Planning BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant PPS as Project Planning Service
participant DB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open Planning Worklist
UI->>BFF: Load worklist
BFF->>ORCH: Get worklist by role
ORCH->>PPS: Fetch planning records
PPS->>DB: Query project_planning by role/status
DB-->>PPS: Planning rows
PPS->>PPS: Derive CTA from current status
PPS-->>ORCH: Worklist response
ORCH-->>BFF: Aggregated response
BFF-->>UI: Show worklist with CTA
